data.description:
Great family home with lots of amenities.  Bedrooms with ample closets, Primary bedroom has double closets and bath with marble  walk in shower.
Kitchen nicely updated with granite and tile backsplashes.   Extra room on front that is a great office space or extra living.  
Must see.
